Welcome to TuneUp Drive Defrag
<h1>Welcome to <nobr>TuneUp Drive Defrag</nobr></h1>

<p>Increasing fragmentation can cause your hard drives to continually slow 
down, because files are no longer stored as a single unit and need to be 
searched at different locations. </p>

<p>If necessary, TuneUp Drive Defrag will defragment your files. This by itself 
will make your computer noticeably faster again.
In addition, TuneUp Drive Defrag organizes your files very intelligently, 
so that Windows and programs start noticeably faster.</p>

<p>You should run TuneUp Drive Defrag regularly to improve the performance of 
your system. The easiest way to do this is by automatic 1-Click Maintenance.</p>